Qiimaynta ugu horreysa ee cudurka COVID-19 ee Febraayo 18, 2020 waxay muujisay in decocation-ka unugyada, sameynta daahyada jeermiska iyo gelitaanka unugyada dhexe iyo unugyada multinucleated synesial ee sambabada bukaanka u dhintay cudurka ay la jaanqaadeen cudurka fayraska iyo ARDS, iyo kuwa SARS iyo MERS.
