14 Febraayo 2020, Feng Zhang Group ayaa sharaxay borotokool loo adeegsado farsamada CRISPR-ku saleysan ee SHERLOCK ee lagu aqoonsado SARS-CoV-2, kaas oo lagu ogaado xargaha SARS-CoV-2 RNA-da synthetic hal saac gudahood iyada oo aan loo baahnayn qalab ballaaran iyadoo la adeegsanayo qashin-qubka oo leh 20 × 10-18 mol/L ilaa 200 × 10-18 mol/L (10-100 koobi halkii microliter ee soo-galka).
Waxaan rajeyneynaa in haddii lagu xaqiijiyo shaybaarada caafimaad, tikniyoolajiyada cusub ay si weyn u kordhin karto dareenka iyo fududeynta.
Iyada oo la'aanta khibradda ee ku saabsan CoVs cusub, dhakhaatiirtu waxay kaliya siin karaan daryeel caawimaad bukaannada COVID-19 waxayna isku dayi karaan daaweyn kala duwan oo hore loo isticmaalay ama la soo jeediyay oo ku saabsan CoVs kale sida SARS-CoV iyo MERS-CoV iyo cudurrada kale ee fayraska (Mashruuca 2).
Daaweyntaas waxaa ka mid ah daaweynta hadda jirta iyo tan mustaqbalka, oo ay ka mid yihiin daawooyinka ka hortagga fayraska, immunosuppressants, steroids, plasma ka soo kabashada bukaanada, daawooyinka Shiinaha iyo taageerada maskaxda.
