Caddaynta hidde-dhaxalka ee dib-u-soo-kabashada dabiiciga ah waxaa laga helay HCoV-HKU1 iyo HCoV-OC43 iyo sidoo kale xayawaanka sida bakaylaha SL-CoV iyo bakaylaha COV-HKU9.
Is dhexgalka Virus-ka iyo fayraska ee la xidhiidha caabuqa
Marka lagu daro saddexda arrimood ee kor lagu soo sheegay, isdhexgalka fayraska ee la leh qaataha cayayaanka waa qodob kale oo muhiim ah oo saameyn ku leh gudbinta noocyada.
Halkan, iskudhafka SARS-CoV waxaa loo qaatay tusaale ahaan, kaas oo sidoo kale muujiyay caddayn xulasho wanaagsan inta lagu jiro dhacdooyinka gudbinta noocyada.
Iyada oo ku saleysan falanqaynta isugeynta ee isugeynta SARS-CoV ee aadanaha iyo dadka rayidka ah, SARS-CoV wuxuu u muuqdaa inuu si dhakhso leh u qaatay isugeyn kala duwan, gaar ahaan isbeddelka RBD ee S protein.
Caadi ahaan, RBD ee S protein, COV waxay la falgalaysaa cellular receptor waxaana si xamaasad leh loogu xulayaa jawaabta antibody ee xayawaanka.
SARS-CoV, RBDs waxay ku jiraan 318th ilaa 510th amino acids ee S1 block, taas oo isku xirta ACE2 aadanaha iyo sidoo kale qaataha si ay u galaan fayraska.
RBD ee SARS-CoV waxay u oggolaaneysaa gudbinta fayraska noocyo kala duwan oo awood u leh inay aqoonsadaan qaataha ACE2 ee xayawaanka kala duwan, oo ay ku jiraan shabeelka, duqsiyada, jiirka iyo eeyaha raccoon.
Xaqiiqdii, RBD-yada kala-soocidda ee aadanaha iyo viruska ayaa laga helay kaliya lix haraaga amino acid oo kala duwan, afar ka mid ahna waxay ku yaalliin qaabka qaataha-xidhka ee isdhexgalka qaataha ACE2.
Cudurka SARS-CoV wuxuu leeyahay mutaantiyada K489N iyo S487T oo ku jira RBD-da, taas oo awood u siin karta isdhexgalka spike protein ee la leh soo-dhoweeyeyaasha ACE2 ee aadanaha.
Taasi waa, bedelka labadan amino acid waxay muhiim u tahay in viruska uu u qaato bini aadamka
Waxaa muhiim ah in la ogaado in SARS-CoV-2 uu wadaagayo qaataha isku midka ah ee SARS-CoV.
Farqiga u dhexeeya SARS-CoV-2 iyo SARS-CoV-3 ee 30% ee S1 unugyada S protein wuxuu tilmaamayaa in rabitaankooda S protein ay la xiriiraan ACE2 ee aadanaha laga yaabo inay isbeddeleen.
