Falanqaynta hidde-wadaha ayaa muujisay in fayraska 'coronavirus' uu isku darsado hidde-wadaha laba nooc oo kala ah jilitaanka 'betacoronavirus' iyo jilitaanka 'subgenus serbicovirus' (lineage B).
Waxay 96% la mid tahay noocyada kale ee bakteeriyada (BatCov RaTG13) heerka genomic.
Febraayo 2020, cilmi baarayaasha Shiinaha waxay ogaadeen in farqiga u dhexeeya fayraska lo'da iyo fayraska aadanaha uu yahay hal amino acid oo keliya qaybo ka mid ah isku xigxiga hidde-wadaha.
Ilaa hadda, 92% walxaha genomic ee la wadaago ee fayraska iyo SARS-CoV-2 ayaa la ogaaday isbarbardhigga genomic oo dhan, taas oo ku filneyn in la caddeeyo in fayraska uu yahay martigeliyaha dhexdhexaadka ah.
Calaamadaha ayaa si ku meelgaar ah u ogaan kara in fayraska uu ku dhacay, laakiin waxaa lagu xaqiijin karaa tijaabooyinka cudurka ee lagu sameeyo falcelinta silsiladda polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) ama sawirada CT.
Daraasad la barbardhigo PCR iyo CT oo lagu sameeyay Wuhan ayaa soo jeedisay in CT, in kasta oo ay ka yar tahay saxnaanta, ay aad uga nugul tahay PCR, iyo in astaamo badan oo ka mid ah astaamaha sawirka ay la mid yihiin cudurrada kale ee sambabada iyo qaababka cudurka.
