Daraasad ballaaran oo lagu sameeyay Shiinaha ayaa la barbardhigay natiijooyinka CT-ga laabta iyo PCR, waxayna muujisay in sawir qaadista, in kasta oo ay ka yar tahay saxnaanta ogaanshaha caabuqa, ay tahay mid dhakhso badan oo xasaasi ah, waxayna soo jeedisay in loo tixgeliyo in loo isticmaalo qalab baaritaan oo loogu talagalay aagagga cudurku ku faafay.
