Bishii Maarso 16, WHO waxay amartay in la kordhiyo barnaamijka baaritaanka sida ugu wanaagsan ee lagu yareeyo faafitaanka COVID-19. Baahida weyn ee baaritaanka ayaa sababtay baahida weyn ee faafitaanka fayraska, taasoo keentay in boqolaal baaritaano ah ay ku sii jiraan shaybaarrada gaarka loo leeyahay ee Mareykanka, iyo in la yareeyo sahayda swabs iyo kiimikada kiimikada.
