Inta badan waxay ku jiraan isopropyl alkol ama ethanol oo lagu sameeyay qaab gel ah oo leh macdan qallajin ah sida carbomer (polymer of acrylic acid) ama dareere qoyan sida glycerin, ama qaab xumbo ah oo sahlan in la isticmaalo oo yareeya saameynta qalajinta khamriga.
