Alkohoolka wuxuu dilaa bakteeriyada nadaafadda, bakteeriyada u adkaysta dawooyinka badan (MRSA iyo VRE), cudurka shuban biyoodka iyo qaar ka mid ah fayraska (oo ay ku jiraan HIV, hargabka, RSV, rhinovirus, vaccina, influenza iyo hepatitis) iyo fangaska
Alkohoolka ku jira saafiyaha gacmaha wuxuu ka kooban yahay 70% alkohool wuxuuna dilaa 99.97% (3,5 log cut oo u dhiganta 35 decibel cut) iyo 99.99% ilaa 99.99% (4-5 log cut) jeermiska gacanta 30 ilbiriqsi kadib markii la isticmaalo. Saafiyeyaasha gacmaha ayaa aad ugu waxtar badan jeermiska qaar, qaar kalena waxtar yar ayey u leeyihiin jeermiska.
Qalabka lagu nadiifiyo gacmaha ee ku saleysan khamriga waa mid aan waxtar lahayn oo ka hortagga bakteeriyada sida norovirus (ama norvoc), oo ah sababta ugu badan ee keenta gastroenteritis-ka faafa. Isticmaal gacmo badan oo antiseptic ah ama gacmo-nadiifinta khamriga si aad u nadiifiso gacmahaaga.
