B'angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku xidhan dusha sare ee unugyada wadnaha, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo mindhicirka.
Waxay ka hortageysaa waxqabadka ACE2 ee angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) iyadoo la yareynayo heerka angiotensin-II iyo kor u qaadista heerka Ang ((1-7)) sidaas darteedna waa daawo rajo leh oo lagu daaweynayo cudurada wadnaha iyo dhiigga. ACE2 waxay u adeegtaa sidii meel ay ku galaan unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronaviruses.
Qaybta bini aadamka ee enzyme-ka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaanaa hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 waa metallogen oo zinc ku jira, waxaana laga helaa endothelial iyo unugyada kale ee dusha sare.
ACE2 wuxuu leeyahay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal collectarin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waa borotiin maqaarka ku jira oo ah nooca hal-marinta ah kaas oo kiciya falcelinta enzymes-ka ee unugyada ku jira wadnaha iyo unugyada kale.
Astaamaha dheeriga ah ee ACE2 waxaa laga saaraa transmembrane labaad oo la yiraahdo Shades, waxaana badanaa lagu sii daayaa dhiigga, ugu dambeynna waxaa lagu qasi karaa kaadida.
ACE2 waxay ku jirtaa jir dhinac kasta: waxay ku xidhan tahay qanjidhada unugyada 'alveolar' ee 'type II' ee sambabada, enterocytes-ka xiidmaha yar yar, unugyada 'endothelial' ee xididdada iyo xididdada iyo muruqyada jilicsan ee xididdada badankood.
ACE2 mRNA waxaa sidoo kale laga helaa maskaxda, garabka, hypothalamus iyo garabka.
