ACE2 waxay burburin kartaa dhowr peptides oo kale oo ay ka mid yihiin [des-Arg9]- bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa gaadiidka daasadda ee SLC6A19, oo ah isugeynta amino acid ee dhexdhexaad ah, waxaana lagu daraa cudurka wadnaha.
Sida borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 wuxuu u shaqeeyaa sida barta ugu weyn ee gelitaanka unugyada qaar ka mid ah fayraska corona, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (fayraska keena SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (fayraska keena COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, isku xirnaanta domainka enzymatic ee ACE2 ee dusha sare ee unugyada ee SARS-CoV iyo borotiinka 'spike S1' ee SARS-CoV2 waxay saameyn ku yeelataa endosytosis, iyo wareejinta labada fayras iyo enzyme ee endosomes-ka ku yaal unugyada.
