10 Abriil 2020, Google iyo Apple waxay si wada jir ah u shaaciyeen in shaqeyntu ay ku dhex dari doonto taageerada barnaamijyada ku saleysan Bluetooth si toos ah nidaamyadooda hawlgalka Android iyo iOS.
Dowladda Shiinaha oo ay si wada jir ah ula shaqeyso shirkadda Alipay ee Shiinaha ayaa soo bandhigtay barnaamij ay dadku ku hubin karaan inay la xiriireen dadka qaba COVID-19.
Waxaa laga isticmaalaa in kabadan 200 magaalo oo Shiine ah. Waxaa laga isticmaalaa Singapore barnaamijka Trace Together.
App-ka waxaa soo saaray bulshada IT-ga ee maxalliga ah waxaana loo sameeyay il furan waxaana loo gudbin doonaa dowladda. Waqooyiga Macedonia waxay soo bandhigtay barnaamijka ku saleysan buluuga "Stop Corona" si ay ula xiriirto dadka laga yaabo inay ku dhacaan cudurka iyo saraakiisha daryeelka caafimaadka si ay si dhakhso leh uga jawaabaan.
