Codsiga ayaa ku jira marxaladda horumarinta, waxaana la heli doonaa toddobaadyo gudahood, sida ay sheegtay dowladda 12 -ka Abriil 2020.
Australia iyo New Zealand labaduba waxay ka fekerayaan barnaamijyo ku saleysan Singapore's Trace Together iyo Blue Tooth Protocol. Ruushka wuxuu damacsan yahay inuu soo bandhigo barnaamij geofencing ah oo loogu talagalay bukaannada COVID-19 ee ku nool Moscow, si loo hubiyo inaysan guriga ka bixin.
Ross Anderson, oo ah Professor of Security Engineering ee Jaamacadda Cambridge, ayaa liis garay dhibaatooyin badan oo suurtagal ah oo ku saabsan nidaamyada ku saleysan app, oo ay ka mid yihiin falcelinta qaldan iyo suurtagalnimada waxtarka yar marka isticmaalka app-ka uu ku koobanyahay tiro aad u yar oo dad ah.
