Chloroquine waa daawo ka hortagga shubanka waxaana loo isticmaalaa in lagu daaweeyo cudurrada iswada.
18-kii Maarso, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday in afarta daawo ee lagu baran doono tijaabooyinka is-dhexgalka ee is-dhexgalka ay ka mid yihiin chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine la xiriira.
Gudoomiyaha New York Andrew Cuomo ayaa ku dhawaaqay in tijaabooyinka New York ee chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine ay bilaaban doonaan 24-ka Maarso. 28 -ka Maarso, FDA waxay oggolaatay isticmaalka hydroxychloroquine sulfate iyo chloroquine phosphate ee hoos yimaada Oggolaanshaha Isticmaalka Degdegga ah (EUA).
Daawadan looma oggola FDA-da habka tijaabada caafimaad, waxaana loo oggol yahay EUA-da in lagu sameeyo daaweyn tijaabo ah oo keliya bukaannada la isbitaaloobay laakiin aan heli karin daaweynta tijaabada caafimaad.
CDC waxay sheegtay in "Isticmaalka, qiyaasta, ama muddada loo isticmaalo hydroxychloroquine ee ka hortagga ama daaweynta caabuqa SARS-CoV-2 aan wali la xaqiijin".
Dhakhaatiirta ayaa sheegay in daawada loo isticmaalo marka "aan la helin wax kale oo la dooran karo".
Daraasad yar oo ay sameeyeen koox cilmi baaris ah oo Turki ah oo ku taala Istanbul ayaa lagu daray chlorokivin iyo zinc, vitamin A, vitamin C iyo vitamin D.
Waxbarasho ballaaran ayaa ka socota jaamacadaha Duke iyo Oxford.
